OL,3,CLeicester park murder trial jury sent
OL,4,Chome after judge falls ill
OL,6,FA jury considering verdicts against
OL,7,Ftwo teenagers accused of killing an 80-
OL,8,Fyear-old man has been sent home until
OL,9,FTuesday after the judge in the case
OL,10,Ffell ill.
OL,12,FA 15-year-old boy denies the murder
OL,13,Fand manslaughter of Bhim Kohli, who he
OL,14,Fis alleged to have kicked and punched
OL,15,Fduring a "gratuitous" attack which
OL,16,Fleft him with a broken neck and
OL,17,Ffractured ribs.
