OL,4,Chome after judge falls ill
OL,6,FJurors resumed their deliberations on
OL,7,FMonday morning, but were sent home
OL,8,Fshortly before a scheduled lunch break
OL,9,Fby Mr Justice Turner, who told the
OL,10,Fpanel he was not feeling well.
OL,12,FThe judge said: "Members of the jury,
OL,13,FI have been struggling today ` I am
OL,14,Fnot well and I have held out until
OL,15,Fthis lunchtime.
OL,17,F"I think it's probably best that I
OL,18,Fcall it a day now and see if I can
OL,19,Frecuperate by tomorrow. I'm suffering.
