OL,6,F"I keep my fingers crossed that there
OL,7,Fhas been some improvement in my
OL,8,Fcondition."
OL,10,FAddressing jurors last week,
OL,11,Fprosecutor Harpreet Sandhu KC used his
OL,12,Fclosing speech to accuse the 15-year-
OL,13,Fold youth of having a desire to cause
OL,14,Freally serious physical injury to Mr
OL,15,FKohli.
OL,17,FThe defendant, who denies murder, told
OL,18,Fthe court he "fell on top of" Mr Kohli
OL,19,Fafter the pensioner walked towards him
OL,20,Fsaying something in an angry voice.
